snippet.title: Ex Natura: Nature Corrupted Story Trailer
snippet.description:
Ex Natura : Nature Corrupted is a challenging, action packed, souls-lite experience developed by Blackburne Game Studio. Fight your way from the deepest cultist dungeons to the top of the holy tree and reclaim your throne in this mysterious "pre-human" era themed epic story. 
Walk within the footsteps of Elrih the god of air, to experience the journey he goes through to claim his throne.

📎Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1557180

📍Join us:
